snippet.title: 15 Minutes of Uncut Gameplay (Monogrove) - TDS - Tower Defense Strategy
snippet.description:
TDS - Tower Defense Strategy - is a up to 4-player co-op Tower Defense, Real Time Strategy hybrid made by Blockage as our first game on a new platform!
WISHLIST THE GAME!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2392280/TDS/

Tower Defense Strategy

The version of the game im playing on is the demo version of it. Everything is subject to change quite abit when it actually comes out in early access.

I'm playing like a silly guy, a buffoon some might say. But I did actually mean to end it on a later Tide so consider it pretty legit oopsie!

Blockage is currently a team of two guys making what we think is a 'good time'. There's a lot to this game as you will hopefully soon see when the demo comes out publicly within the next month or so!
